َبَّكُمْ فَاسْتَجَابَ لَكُمْ اَنِّيْ مُمِدُّكُمْ بِاَلْفٍ مِّنَ الْمَلٰۤىِٕكَةِ مُرْدِفِيْنَ</span><span class="__className_2abdee block text-md lg:text-lg text-primary-500 mb-3 sm:mt-3 sm:mb-4 dark:text-primary-300">idz tastaghîtsûna rabbakum fastajâba lakum annî mumiddukum bi&#x27;alfim minal-malâ&#x27;ikati murdifîn</span><span class="block text-md lg:text-lg text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">(Ingatlah) ketika kamu memohon pertolongan kepada Tuhanmu, lalu Dia mengabulkan(-nya) bagimu (seraya berfirman), “Sesungguhnya Aku akan mendatangkan bala bantuan kepadamu berupa seribu malaikat yang datang berturut-turut.”</span></div></div></div><div class=" last:border-none border-b border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800 py-3 px-3 md:px-5 flex flex-col " id="10"><div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2"><span class=" text-primary-400 dark:text-primary-300 text-xl md:text-2xl">10<!-- -->.</span><div class="nui-ActionVerse "><div class="flex space-x-2.5 rtl:space-x-reverse items-center"><a href="/al-anfal/10" class="__className_80e47c text-sm px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full border border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-600 hover:bg-neutral-300 hover:dark:bg-neutral-600 hover">Tafsir</a><div class="nui-ButtonPlay select-none "><div class="inline-flex items-center py-0.5 cursor-pointer rounded-full transition-all"><span class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 hover:bg-neutral-200 dark:hover:bg-neutral-900 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon" class="w-5 h-5"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.5 5.653c0-1.427 1.529-2.33 2.779-1.643l11.54 6.347c1.295.712 1.295 2.573 0 3.286L7.28 19.99c-1.25.687-2.779-.217-2.779-1.643V5.653Z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></div></div><div><div class="inline-block text-left" data-headlessui-state><button class="text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 flex it