ront mais ils leur seront cause de regret. Puis ils seront vaincus, et ceux qui auront mécru seront vers la Géhenne rassemblés en foule,\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":2,\"end\":4},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":29,\"end\":33},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":69,\"end\":74},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":96,\"end\":100},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":112,\"end\":114},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":142,\"end\":147},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":147,\"end\":149},{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":186,\"end\":189},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":201,\"end\":203},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":215,\"end\":217}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":35}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"36\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":1197,\"number\":37,\"text\":\"لِيَمِيْزَ اللّٰهُ الْخَبِيْثَ مِنَ الطَّيِّبِ وَيَجْعَلَ الْخَبِيْثَ بَعْضَهٗ عَلٰى بَعْضٍ فَيَرْكُمَهٗ جَمِيْعًا فَيَجْعَلَهٗ فِيْ جَهَنَّمَۗ  اُولٰۤىِٕكَ هُمُ الْخٰسِرُوْنَࣖ\",\"translation_id\":\"agar Allah memisahkan (golongan) yang buruk dari yang baik dan menjadikan (golongan) yang buruk itu sebagiannya di atas yang lain, lalu Dia menumpukkan semuanya. Kemudian, Dia menjadikannya ke dalam (neraka) Jahanam. Mereka itulah orang-orang yang rugi.\",\"juz_id\":9,\"surah_id\":8,\"transliteration\":\"liyamîzallâhul-khabîtsa minath-thayyibi wa yaj‘alal-khabîtsa ba‘dlahû ‘alâ ba‘dlin fa yarkumahû jamî‘an fa yaj‘alahû fî jahannam, ulâ'ika humul-khâsirûn\",\"translation_en\":\"[It is] so that Allāh may distinguish the wicked from the good and place the wicked some of them upon others and heap them all together and put them into Hell. It is those who are the losers.\",\"translation_de\":\"damit Allah das Schlechte vom Guten sondere und das Schlechte übereinander tue, es alles zusammenhäufe und in die Hölle bringe. Das sind die Verlierer.\",\"translation_tr\":\"(Bu toplama) Allah'ın murdarı temizden ayıklaması (mümini kâfirden ayırması) ve bütün murdarların bir kısmını diğer bir kısmının üstüne koyup hepsini yığarak cehenneme atması içindir. İşte onlar ziyana uğrayanların kendileridir.\",\"translation_fr\":\"pour qu’Allah sépare (celui qui est) mauvais de (celui qui est) bon et entasse les mauvais les uns sur les autres pour en faire un seul amas qu’Il précipitera dans la Géhenne. Ceux-là sont bien les perdants.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":51,\"end\":52},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":89,\"end\":94},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":111,\"end\":113},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":114,\"end\":116},{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":119,\"end\":120},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":137,\"end\":139},{\"class\":\"madd-wajib\",\"start\":148,\"end\":152},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":171,\"end\":173}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":36}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"37\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":1198,\"number\":38,\"text\":\"قُلْ لِّلَّذِيْنَ كَفَرُوْٓا اِنْ يَّنْتَهُوْا يُغْفَرْ لَهُمْ مَّا قَدْ سَلَفَۚ وَاِنْ يَّعُوْدُوْا فَقَدْ مَضَتْ سُنَّتُ الْاَوَّلِيْنَ\",\"translation_id\":\"Katakanlah (Nabi Muhammad) kepada orang-orang yang kufur itu, “Jika mereka berhenti (dari kekufurannya dan masuk Islam), niscaya akan diampuni dosa-dosa mereka yang telah lalu. Jika mereka kembali lagi (memerangi Nabi), sungguh berlaku (kepada mereka) sunah (aturan Allah untuk menjatuhkan sanksi atas) orang-orang terdahulu.”\",\"juz_id\":9,\"surah_id\":8,\"transliteration\":\"qul lilladzîna kafarû iy yantahû yughfar lahum mâ qad salaf, wa iy ya‘ûdû fa qad madlat sunnatul-awwalîn\",\"translation_en\":\"Say to those who have disbelieved [that] if they cease, what has previously occurred will be forgiven for them. But if they return [to hostility] - then the precedent of the former [rebellious] peoples has already taken place.\",\"translation_de\":\"Sag zu denen, die ungläubig sind: Wenn sie aufhören, wird ihnen vergeben, was bereits vergangen ist. Wenn sie aber (dazu) zurückkehren, - so hat sich schon die Gesetzmäßigkeit an den Früheren vollzogen.\",\"translation_tr\":\"İnkâr edenlere, (sana düşmanlıktan) vazge