ge-leur un traitement tel qu’il dissuaderait ceux qui les suivent, peut-être se souviendront-ils.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":4,\"end\":6},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":17,\"end\":19},{\"class\":\"qalqalah\",\"start\":46,\"end\":47},{\"class\":\"idgham-mimi\",\"start\":53,\"end\":58},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":95,\"end\":97}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":56}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"57\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":1218,\"number\":58,\"text\":\"وَاِمَّا تَخَافَنَّ مِنْ قَوْمٍ خِيَانَةً فَانْۢبِذْ اِلَيْهِمْ عَلٰى سَوَاۤءٍۗ اِنَّ اللّٰهَ لَا يُحِبُّ الْخَاۤىِٕنِيْنَࣖ\",\"translation_id\":\"Jika engkau (Nabi Muhammad) benar-benar khawatir (akan terjadi) pengkhianatan dari suatu kaum, kembalikanlah (perjanjian itu) kepada mereka dengan cara seimbang (adil dan jujur). Sesungguhnya Allah tidak menyukai para pengkhianat.\",\"juz_id\":10,\"surah_id\":8,\"transliteration\":\"wa immâ takhâfanna ming qaumin khiyânatan fambidz ilaihim ‘alâ sawâ', innallâha lâ yuḫibbul-khâ'inîn\",\"translation_en\":\"If you [have reason to] fear from a people betrayal, throw [their treaty] back to them, [putting you] on equal terms. Indeed, Allāh does not like traitors.\",\"translation_de\":\"Und wenn du dann von irgendwelchen Leuten Verrat befürchtest, so verwirf ihnen (die Verpflichtung) in gleicher Weise. Gewiß, Allah liebt nicht die Verräter.\",\"translation_tr\":\"(Antlaşma yaptığın) bir kavmin hainlik yapmasından korkarsan, sen de (onlarla yaptığın ahdi) aynı şekilde bozduğunu kendilerine bildir. Çünkü Allah, hainleri sevmez.\",\"translation_fr\":\"Et si tu appréhendes quelque félonie de la part d’un peuple, alors dénonce ouvertement et loyalement le pacte qui vous lie, car Allah n’aime pas les traîtres.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":4,\"end\":6},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":16,\"end\":18},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":22,\"end\":27},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":39,\"end\":44},{\"class\":\"iqlab\",\"start\":45,\"end\":47},{\"class\":\"iqla